<div class="thumbinner" style="width:252px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Mothers%27_Day_Cake.jpg" class="image" title="Mothers' Day Cake.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8e/Mothers%27_Day_Cake.jpg/250px-Mothers%27_Day_Cake.jpg" width="250" height="188" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
